snippet.title: Live: Amber Vilhauer and John Lee Dumas on Building Influence, Podcasting and Speaking!
snippet.description:
Catch this PHENOMENAL interview with John Lee Dumas~ Founder of the top business podcast Entrepreneur On Fire (which now has more than 2,000 episodes published and more than 10 million downloads! ~

What I asked John:

🔥 What are some specific moves you made to make the leap from successful podcasting influencer, to successful speaker?

🔥 What are a few things entrepreneurs (who want to be well-paid speakers and influencers) need to do to get on bigger stages for bigger fees?

🔥 With thousands of successful and high-impact podcast episodes behind you (both with your being the interviewer and interviewee), how specifically can authors use podcasting as a tool for marketing and launch?

🔥 Do you have any hacks or tricks to recommend that gets you in position to interview or be on stage with someone, or even talk with someone that once felt unreachable? What could I do to get myself in the door with a significant influencer?

🔥 What are any last suggestions you'd have so that our listeners can prepare for the most significant launch possible?

I've known John for six years now (wha?!) and I can tell you that he is truly one of the most genuine, caring, intelligent, creative people I know. He's THE REAL DEAL folks!

John's bio if you live on Mars and haven't heard of him yet lol: https://www.eofire.com/about/

Join his list, BUY the FREEDOM JOURNAL (awesome), and check out all of his other resources, wow, https://www.eofire.com/resources/

You don't want to miss this Live Stream episode which supports YOUR next launch... as the countdown continues toward our AuthorUpLive.com event June3-4 (AuthorUpLive.com). 🔥🔥🔥🔥
